{"tid":2052293,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"失戀最痛心係有太多美好回憶，而你冇好好珍惜佢","createTime":"2020-06-05T12:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T17:33:33.000Z","uid":107157,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b07518a424a4b36572a29e3fd8fca87c06fd1587","tid":2052293,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:05:38.000Z","msg":"每一段越幸福，越美好，傷得就越深。<br />\n對方天真，單純，無條件為你付出，自己有錢唔介意你窮，自己高學歷唔介意你廢，唔介意同你組織一個家庭。而你就一路自卑，一路傷害佢，拒絕佢一次又一次既鼓勵。最後，個心已經累透，選擇離開你。回頭一睇，分開對佢已經唔係一回事，而傷心既人只係得返你一個人。<br />\n<br />\n對方對你太好，你就知道下一段感情，下一個一定冇ex咁好。慢慢你就對愛情唔抱有期望，唔再重視愛情。<br />\n<br />\n一切都係自作自受。"},{"pid":"630ab333c7b34d84a43e83422f1b083eca0073a5","tid":2052293,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:09:16.000Z","msg":"我係仆街仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ae16ed72a45554f5d1bb97aca12b7ca40a7277","tid":2052293,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T13:01:24.000Z","msg":"揀得你<br />\n自咩卑姐"},{"pid":"24a87efee05a3648cbb8b0e5b316628bb2790344","tid":2052293,"uid":100596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"講中曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded5e627112e7b9c7dec68cba99875424838a296","tid":2052293,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24a87efee05a3648cbb8b0e5b316628bb2790344","tid":2052293,"uid":100596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"講中曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T13:41:32.000Z","msg":"睇黎係前輩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"h